      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-00707'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040126_GCR_172'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-phillips' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040126_GCR_172' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Phillips' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
